            "question": "1. What shipping methods do you offer?",
            "answer": "<p>We provide complimentary standard shipping through trusted carriers such as UPS or DHL. Delivery typically takes 10–14 business days.</p><p>All shipments are fully insured, trackable, and require an adult signature upon delivery to ensure the safe arrival of your jewelry.</p><p><strong>For International Customers:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>United States:</strong> Customs duties are covered by us.<br/></li><li><strong>Other Countries:</strong> Import duties, VAT, and clearance charges may apply according to your country’s regulations. These fees are not included in our pricing and remain the buyer’s responsibility.</li></ul>"
          }
