            "question": "2. Do you provide third-party diamond certification?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, we offer third-party certification for selected diamond pieces from respected gemological laboratories such as IGI, HRD, IDGL, GIN, and SGL.</p><p></p><p>If you would like certification included with your purchase, please contact us prior to placing your order so we can assist you accordingly.</p>"
