            "answer": "<p>To maintain the brilliance of your jewelry:</p><ul><li>Soak the piece in warm water mixed with mild dish soap (10:2 ratio) for up to 3 hours.<br/></li><li>Gently clean using a soft brush.<br/></li><li>Rinse thoroughly with clean water.<br/></li><li>Pat dry with a soft cloth (avoid paper towels).<br/></li><li>Use a jewelry polishing cloth for additional shine.<br/></li><li>Avoid exposure to bleach, harsh chemicals, or abrasive cleaners.<br/></li></ul><p>Proper care will help preserve the beauty of your jewelry for years to come.</p>"
